    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212000/extras/b31e9095f9f10eb7cc1592f27d7e318a.avif?t=1740347602\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212000/extras_big/b31e9095f9f10eb7cc1592f27d7e318a.avif?t=1740347602 width=800 height=566 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shovel &amp; Swindle is a co-op game where you and a friend explore a graveyard among other locations and rob its graves to earn money while avoiding the guards and uncovering many secrets. Make sure you balance exploring and gaining money to progress.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by Burke &amp; Hare, you'll go into a graveyard with the sole intention of robbing graves either alone or with a friend... But there's more than what meets the eye!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore interconnected levels full of secrets and shortcuts, but be wary of the  bobbies, if they catch you, that's it for the night!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the money you gain to upgrade your base and purchase tools to help you in your gravedigging escapades.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncover the secrets hidden right before your eyes to obtain what you desire most.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212000/extras/fc633a3ed18171a673cddf48cd2b03d9.avif?t=1740347602\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3212000/extras_big/fc633a3ed18171a673cddf48cd2b03d9.avif?t=1740347602 width=800 height=800 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
